We will need to add some site features that become useful only when the site contains so many nodes that they overlap often, and graphs become less navigable

- Graph pruning on-render with option to expand to see more. If anyone can add to the graph, it will quickly become full of unhelpful one-off node connections that are irrelevant or already considered elsewhere in the graph. 

- Implement forking and merging


"Source investigation" where a source is allowed to have an entire graph to prove or disprove it. 